VYDBUr YHVH 'aL-MShH L'aMUr.
DBUr 'aL-BNY YShUr'aL V'aMUrTh 'aLHM 'aYSh KY YPhL'a NDUr B'yUrKK NPhShTh LYHVH.
VHYH 'yUrKK HZKUr MBN 'yShUrYM ShNH V'yD BN-ShShYM ShNH VHYH 'yUrKK ChMShYM ShQL KSPh BShQL HQDSh.
V'aM-NQBH HV'a VHYH 'yUrKK ShLShYM ShQL.
V'aM MBN-ChMSh ShNYM V'yD BN-'yShUrYM ShNH VHYH 'yUrKK HZKUr 'yShUrYM ShQLYM VLNQBH 'yShUrTh ShQLYM.
V'aM MBN-ChDSh V'yD BN-ChMSh ShNYM VHYH 'yUrKK HZKUr ChMShH ShQLYM KSPh VLNQBH 'yUrKK ShLShTh ShQLYM KSPh.
V'aM MBN-ShShYM ShNH VM'yLH 'aM-ZKUr VHYH 'yUrKK ChMShH 'yShUr ShQL VLNQBH 'yShUrH ShQLYM.
V'aM-MK HV'a M'yUrKK VH'yMYDV LPhNY HKHN VH'yUrYK 'aThV HKHN 'yL-PhY 'aShUr ThShYG YD HNDUr Y'yUrYKNV HKHN.
V'aM-BHMH 'aShUr YQUrYBV MMNH QUrBN LYHVH KL 'aShUr YThN MMNV LYHVH YHYH-QDSh.
L'a YChLYPhNV VL'a-YMYUr 'aThV TVB BUr'y 'aV-Ur'y BTVB V'aM-HMUr YMYUr BHMH BBHMH VHYH-HV'a VThMVUrThV YHYH-QDSh.
V'aM KL-BHMH TM'aH 'aShUr L'a-YQUrYBV MMNH QUrBN LYHVH VH'yMYD 'aTh- HBHMH LPhNY HKHN.
VH'yUrYK HKHN 'aThH BYN TVB VBYN Ur'y K'yUrKK HKHN KN YHYH.
V'aM-G'aL YG'aLNH VYSPh ChMYShThV 'yL-'yUrKK.
V'aYSh KY-YQDSh 'aTh-BYThV QDSh LYHVH VH'yUrYKV HKHN BYN TVB VBYN Ur'y K'aShUr Y'yUrYK 'aThV HKHN KN YQVM.
V'aM-HMQDYSh YG'aL 'aTh-BYThV VYSPh ChMYShYTh KSPh-'yUrKK 'yLYV VHYH LV.
V'aM MShDH 'aChZThV YQDYSh 'aYSh LYHVH VHYH 'yUrKK LPhY ZUr'yV ZUr'y ChMUr Sh'yUrYM BChMShYM ShQL KSPh.
'aM-MShNTh HYBL YQDYSh ShDHV K'yUrKK YQVM.
V'aM-'aChUr HYBL YQDYSh ShDHV VChShB-LV HKHN 'aTh-HKSPh 'yL-PhY HShNYM HNVThUrTh 'yD ShNTh HYBL VNGUr'y M'yUrKK.
V'aM-G'aL YG'aL 'aTh-HShDH HMQDYSh 'aThV VYSPh ChMShYTh KSPh-'yUrKK 'yLYV VQM LV.
V'aM-L'a YG'aL 'aTh-HShDH V'aM-MKUr 'aTh-HShDH L'aYSh 'aChUr L'a YG'aL 'yVD.
VHYH HShDH BTSh'aThV BYBL QDSh LYHVH KShDH HChUrM LKHN ThHYH 'aChZThV.
V'aM 'aTh-ShDH MQNThV 'aShUr L'a MShDH 'aChZThV YQDYSh LYHVH.
VChShB-LV HKHN 'aTh MKSTh H'yUrKK 'yD ShNTh HYBL VNThN 'aTh-H'yUrKK BYVM HHV'a QDSh LYHVH.
BShNTh HYVBL YShVB HShDH L'aShUr QNHV M'aThV L'aShUr-LV 'aChZTh H'aUrTSh.
VKL-'yUrKK YHYH BShQL HQDSh 'yShUrYM GUrH YHYH HShQL.
'aK-BKVUr 'aShUr-YBKUr LYHVH BBHMH L'a-YQDYSh 'aYSh 'aThV 'aM-ShVUr 'aM-ShH LYHVH HV'a.
V'aM BBHMH HTM'aH VPhDH B'yUrKK VYSPh ChMShThV 'yLYV V'aM-L'a YG'aL VNMKUr B'yUrKK.
'aK-KL-ChUrM 'aShUr YChUrM 'aYSh LYHVH MKL-'aShUr-LV M'aDM VBHMH VMShDH 'aChZThV L'a YMKUr VL'a YG'aL KL-ChUrM QDSh-QDShYM HV'a LYHVH.
KL-ChUrM 'aShUr YChUrM MN-H'aDM L'a YPhDH MVTh YVMTh.
VKL-M'yShUr H'aUrTSh MZUr'y H'aUrTSh MPhUrY H'yTSh LYHVH HV'a QDSh LYHVH.
V'aM-G'aL YG'aL 'aYSh MM'yShUrV ChMShYThV YSPh 'yLYV.
VKL-M'yShUr BQUr VTSh'aN KL 'aShUr-Y'yBUr ThChTh HShBT H'yShYUrY YHYH-QDSh LYHVH.
L'a YBQUr BYN-TVB LUr'y VL'a YMYUrNV V'aM-HMUr YMYUrNV VHYH-HV'a VThMVUrThV YHYH-QDSh L'a YG'aL.
'aLH HMTShVTh 'aShUr TShVH YHVH 'aTh-MShH 'aL-BNY YShUr'aL BHUr SYNY.
